    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a brand new adventure! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in great shape for its next owner. It drives like a dream and has been really well-maintained over the years. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
