    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS timing for exceptional throttle response. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed manual Getrag transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers for improved damping rates. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain rigidity remain sharp, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
