    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi everyone! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this awesome car! It's in really nice shape and has served me so well over the years. It\u2019s super reliable, drives smoothly, and is ready for many more adventures. If you're looking for a solid, dependable ride that\u2019s been well-cared for, this is definitely the one for you! Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it! \u2728",
