    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This driver-spec example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains tight and the suspension is upgraded with Bilstein dampers for superior damping control. This is a high-performance machine optimized for the purist who values mechanical integrity and throttle response over concours perfection.",
